Package: macde-defaults
Version: 0.2.0
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Sergio <sergio@example.com>
Depends: gdm3
Description: GNOME defaults for a macOS-inspired Debian install
 Applies system-wide GNOME defaults with WhiteSur theming, dock behavior,
 fonts, and hardware tweaks for Intel MacBook 2011-2012 systems.
